TY  - JOUR
T1  - The Formulation of Credit Policy Models
AU  - Mehta, Dileep
Y1  - 1968/10/01
PY  - 1968
DA  - 1968/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.15.2.B30
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.15.2.B30
